<script>
import axios from 'axios'
import { reactive } from 'vue'

export default {
    setup() {
        let images = reactive({
            list: []
        })

        axios.get('http://localhost:3000/homepage/dragon/ball').then((res) => {
            images.list = res.data.data
        })

        console.log(images)

        return {
            images
        }
    }
}
</script>
